20/* TARGET_OS_CPP_BUILTINS() common to all NetBSD targets. */
21#define NETBSD_OS_CPP_BUILTINS_COMMON() \
22 do \
23 { \
24 builtin_define ("__NetBSD__"); \
25 builtin_define ("__unix__"); \
26 builtin_define ("__syslog_attribute__"); \
27 builtin_assert ("system=bsd"); \
28 builtin_assert ("system=unix"); \
29 builtin_assert ("system=NetBSD"); \
30 } \
31 while (0)
32
33/* CPP_SPEC parts common to all NetBSD targets. */
34#define NETBSD_CPP_SPEC \
35 "%{posix:-D_POSIX_SOURCE} \
36 %{pthread:-D_REENTRANT -D_PTHREADS}"
37
38/* NETBSD_NATIVE is defined when gcc is integrated into the NetBSD
39 source tree so it can be configured appropriately without using
40 the GNU configure/build mechanism.
41
42 NETBSD_TOOLS is defined when gcc is built as cross-compiler for
43 the in-tree toolchain.
44 */
45
46#if defined(NETBSD_NATIVE) || defined(NETBSD_TOOLS)

97/* Provide a LIB_SPEC appropriate for NetBSD. Here we:
98
99 1. Select the appropriate set of libs, depending on whether we're
100 profiling.
101
102 2. Include the pthread library if -pthread is specified (only
103 if threads are enabled).
104
105 3. Include the posix library if -posix is specified.
106
107 FIXME: Could eliminate the duplication here if we were allowed to
108 use string concatenation. */
109
110#define NETBSD_LIB_SPEC_PTHREAD \
111 "%{pthread: \
112 %{!p: \
113 %{!pg:-lpthread}} \
114 %{p:-lpthread_p} \
115 %{pg:-lpthread_p}}"
116
117#define NETBSD_LIB_SPEC \
118 NETBSD_LIB_SPEC_PTHREAD \
119 "%{posix: \
120 %{!p: \
121 %{!pg:-lposix}} \
122 %{p:-lposix_p} \
123 %{pg:-lposix_p}} \
124 %{shared: \
125 %{!p: \
126 %{!pg:-lc}} \
127 %{p:-lc_p} \
128 %{pg:-lc_p}} \
129 %{!shared: \
130 %{!symbolic: \
131 %{!p: \
132 %{!pg:-lc}} \
133 %{p:-lc_p} \
134 %{pg:-lc_p}}}"
135
136#undef LIB_SPEC
137#define LIB_SPEC NETBSD_LIB_SPEC
138
139#define LIBSTDCXX_PROFILE "stdc++_p"
140#define MATH_LIBRARY_PROFILE "m_p"
141
142/* Provide a LIBGCC_SPEC appropriate for NetBSD. */
143#ifdef NETBSD_NATIVE
144#define NETBSD_LIBGCC_SPEC \
145 "%{!symbolic: \
146 %{!shared: \
147 %{!p: \
148 %{!pg: -lgcc}}} \
149 %{shared: -lgcc_pic} \
150 %{p: -lgcc_p} \
151 %{pg: -lgcc_p}}"
152#else
153#define NETBSD_LIBGCC_SPEC "-lgcc"
154#endif
155

173/* When building shared libraries, the initialization and finalization
174 functions for the library are .init and .fini respectively. */
175
176#define COLLECT_SHARED_INIT_FUNC(STREAM,FUNC) \
177 do { \
178 fprintf ((STREAM), "void __init() __asm__ (\".init\");"); \
179 fprintf ((STREAM), "void __init() {\n\t%s();\n}\n", (FUNC)); \
180 } while (0)
181
182#define COLLECT_SHARED_FINI_FUNC(STREAM,FUNC) \
183 do { \
184 fprintf ((STREAM), "void __fini() __asm__ (\".fini\");"); \
185 fprintf ((STREAM), "void __fini() {\n\t%s();\n}\n", (FUNC)); \
186 } while (0)
187
188#undef TARGET_POSIX_IO
189#define TARGET_POSIX_IO
